            <title>[THRIFT-5671] libthrift 0.17.0 has no dependencies in POM on central</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-5671</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href=&quot;https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/thrift/libthrift/0.17.0/libthrift-0.17.0.pom&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;libthrift-0.17.0.pom&lt;/a&gt; file downloaded from Maven Central does not have any &amp;lt;dependencies&amp;gt; section. Thus, the transitive dependencies are not included in my build.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
